(8, 2, '苹果“碰瓷”华为？iPhone12确认9月15日发布，库克太高明', '关键字1,关键字2,关键字3', '说明演示文字8', '苹果官方正式确认iPhone12将在9月15日（北京时间9月16日）发布，果粉期待已久的iPhone12终于要来了，苹果也憋不住了。', '0', 'http://demo.wuwenhui.cn/uploads/20200909/adfab2f29a79787a623e3438cfa78704.jpg', 1, '2020-09-09', '<p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">苹果官方正式确认iPhone12将在9月15日（北京时间9月16日）发布，果粉期待已久的iPhone12终于要来了，苹果也憋不住了。不过看到这个时间，大家有没有想到什么？没错，华为将在9月15日这一天面临一个历史性的时刻，麒麟芯片无法继续生产，第三方芯片也不能购买，苹果选择在这个时间发布iPhone12系列，可以说是火药味十足，这是要“碰瓷”华为吗？</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12435051722/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">苹果可以顺利发布iPhone12系列，而华为mate40系列很可能推迟发布。华为官方消息在9月10日的开发者大会中，只提到了HMS Core5.0、鸿蒙OS2.0和EMUI11，并没有关于华为mate40的消息，看来外界的说法也不是没有道理的。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12435051737/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">即便是华为在9月10日宣布华为mate40的发布时间，很有可能会落后iPhone12的发布会时间，这次被苹果半路杀出，成功截胡。苹果这次成功“碰瓷”。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">华为难道还不怒吗？如果华为mate40率先发布，就可以趁早占领市场，先发制人。不过这也不是绝对的，华为做事都是稳扎稳打的，这次的华为mate40说不定可以后发制人也说不定。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">要说的是，华为这次只能“哑巴吃黄连，有苦说不出”，如果没有这次制裁，华为的整个计划会提前很多，也不至于现在连麒麟9000都没有发布。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12435051723/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">库克这次选择的时间点非常高明，众所周知的原因，大家都对9月15日这个时间非常敏感。据数据统计，关于“9月15日”的搜索量高达数十万次，说明大家都是非常关心华为在这一天有何最新动态。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12435051724/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">库克这是要开始正面刚华为了，不管是巧合还是有意，iPhone12的发布会时间已经确认，留给华为mate40的时间已经不多了，希望华为mate40可以带给消费者更多的惊喜，打一个漂亮的翻身仗。</span></p>', 0, 1617244980),
(9, 3, '中国移动中期经营业绩平稳：战略转型效果明显、5G提速', '关键字1,关键字2,关键字3', '说明演示文字9', '中国移动发布2020年中期业绩，营运收入为3899亿元，同比增长0.1%。其中通信服务收入为3582亿元，同比增长1.9%；净利润为558亿元，同比下降0.5%。', '1', 'http://demo.wuwenhui.cn/uploads/20200909/67898e2d7ec95a58aa16f5b34efd92fe.jpg', 1, '2020-09-09', '<p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">中国移动发布2020年中期业绩，营运收入为3899亿元，同比增长0.1%。其中通信服务收入为3582亿元，同比增长1.9%；净利润为558亿元，同比下降0.5%。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">中国移动执行董事兼董事长杨杰表示，在2020 年已过去的几个月中，努力推动业务发展从通信服务向信息服务拓展延伸、业务市场从聚焦移动市场向个人、家庭、政企、 新兴“四轮”市场全向发力、发展方式从资源要素驱动向创新驱动转型升级。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">独立通信分析师付亮对经济观察网表示，今年面对突如其来的疫情，中国移动在积极转型，让他印象较为深刻的是，公司开始注重内容，包括咪咕内容，合作伙伴内容等，通过5G套餐权益等方式提升用户对内容服务的感知，希望能在这个领域获得新的机会，在获取新用户同时也能获得新收入。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">战略转型效果明显</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">被视为蓝海行业的政企市场，成为中国移动的收入增长的主要动力。上半年移动云收入达到人民币44.6亿元，同比增长556.4%。同时，中国移动进一步深化政企体系改革， 以客户需求为导向，完善产品研发体系和服务支撑体系。上半年政企客户数达到1,129 万家，较2019年底净增101万家;DICT收入达到人民币209 亿元，同比增长55.3%。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">在个人市场方面，中国移动发挥5G作用，坚持资费先行、终端先行，强化机套匹配，加速客户向5G迁转，推动5G发展。截至2020年6月底，移动客户达到9.47亿户，其中4G客户达到7.60亿户，5G套餐客户达到7020 万户。上半年，移动ARPU为50.3元，同比下降3.7%，降幅进一步收窄; 手机上网DOU提升39.7%，达到8.6GB。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">在家庭市场方面，中国移动向智慧家庭运营迈进。一方面，坚持“千兆引领”，建设千兆宽带网络；另一方面，开展端到端质量优化。同时注重价值变现，深化智慧家庭运营。中国移动推动“魔百和”、智能组网、家庭安防、智能语音遥控器等智慧家庭业务。上半年，家庭宽带客户净增895万户，达到1.81亿户。“魔百和”用户达到1.3亿户，渗透率达到72.1%。家庭宽带综合ARPU达到人民币35.4元，同比增长1.0%，持续提升。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">此外，在新兴市场方面，国际业务、股权投资、数字内容、金融科技等四大领域是中国移动转型升级的重要承载。上半年国际业务收入达到56.5亿元，同比增长26.1%；上半年，咪咕视频月活跃用户同比增长114.8%，视频彩铃用户超1亿，和包月活跃用户同比增长92.2%。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">按下5G“快进键”</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">“今年上半年是5G的准备期，目前在北上广等大城市三大运营商进程还是比较快的，其他地区的进程差距较大。”付亮称，但是实际覆盖面积还是非常有限的。从投资到商用，到用户再到收入需要周期。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">财报显示，上半年中国移动5G相关资本开支552亿元，全年计划约1050亿元。5G套餐客户达到7020万户。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">中国移动计划全年新建30万个5G基站，在全国所有地级市以上城市提供商用服务，推动SA核心网年内实现商用。截至2020年6月底，中国移动在中国超过50个城市累计开通了18.8万个5G基站，提供商用服务。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">据悉，中国移动在5G成功实现“5G上珠峰”和“5G下深矿”，在产业标准方面，积极参与并推动全面支持5G场景的R16国际标准及时发布，加快推进SA标准成熟。为实现年内SA规模商用，推进5G SA核心网建设。上半年母公司与中国广播电视网络有限公司签订了5G共建共享合作框架协议，双方在网络合建、开放共享、内容渠 道等多领域的合作中进一步细化落地。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">在推动5G建设的同时，中国移动还更加注重加速5G的应用推广，推出超高清直播、 云游戏、云VR等特色业务。值得注意的是，今年中国移动还发布了5G消息白皮书，以探索5G应用的运营新模式、消息新生态和流量新入口，目前5G新消息在部分地区已开展现网试点。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">面向垂直行业客户，中国移动推出5G智慧工厂、智慧电力、智慧钢铁、智慧港口、智慧矿山等15个重点细分行业解决方案。同时，加快构建5G平台和通用能力，布局了OneCity智慧城市、 工业互联网等九大行业平台，初步完成了5G专网产品化，并发布了5G模组“扬帆计划”。</span></p>', 0, 1617244985);
INSERT INTO `__PREFIX__wwh_news` (`id`, `newscategoryid`, `newsname`, `n_keywords`, `n_description`, `summary`, `tjdata`, `image`, `weigh`, `time`, `content`, `views`, `updatetime`) VALUES
(10, 3, '美国选择用中频段建设5G，这不仅是华为的成功，更是美国的大溃败', '关键字1,关键字2,关键字3', '说明演示文字10', '说到5G，可能大家已经并不陌生了，毕竟5G网络在我国已经开始商用，根据公开的数据显示，我国5G用户已经达到一亿。', '0', 'http://demo.wuwenhui.cn/uploads/20200909/17c6b5395b19101bfa3d81b0f1eeda38.png', 1, '2020-09-09', '<p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">美国选择用中频段建设5G</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">说到5G，可能大家已经并不陌生了，毕竟5G网络在我国已经开始商用，根据公开的数据显示，我国5G用户已经达到一亿。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">但是说到我们标题中提到的中频段，可能很多人就不太了解了。简单来说，无论是哪一代的无线网络，都需要工作在特定的频段之上，5G网络的不同之处在于，其工作的频段则有着高频段和中低频段的不同选择。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而所谓的高频段，就是我们经常听到的毫米波频段，而中低频段，就是Sub-6GHz频段。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/3344099630/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">目前全球参与到5G网络建设的国家已经上百，但是在选择采用的频段上，在大国和强国之中，只有美国选择了高频毫米波频段建设5G网络，当然，这主要有这么几个方面的原因。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第一、美国中低频段资源匮乏</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">美国积极采用高频毫米波，而放弃中低频段，与其在中低频段的资源匮乏有关，因为中低频段已经被美国军方占据，因此没有多余的频谱可以划分出来用于5G商用。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这方面有两个案例可以作为说明，首先就是发生在今年四月份，美国联邦通信委员会，内部批准了美国一家小公司，利用L波段建设地面5G网络的申请，但是却遭到了美国军方的反对，主要原因就在于，美国军方担心会影响其使用的GPS信号。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第二个案例，就是美国选择在3.5GHz频段上，利用共享技术，希望推动美国的5G网络在中低频段的建设，但是响应者寥寥，具体原因或许与技术的不成熟有关，因为之前有报道称，美国国防部出资270万美元，资助对频谱共享技术的研究。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/11447878564/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第二、美国在毫米波产业上有优势</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">我们知道，现在是一个地球村时代，是一个经济全球化时代，一家企业的最终产品，其所需要的零配件，可能来自几十上百家供应商的供货，在无线网络市场也是如此。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">电信运营商建设5G网络，就需要电信设备商提供设备，而电信设备商，也需要供应链提供相关的零配件，而美国的很多上游供应商，在毫米波部件上具备优势，因此如果美国成功的引领全球建设毫米波5G网络，无疑会对美国的科技企业利好，占据更多的市场空间，也能帮助美国在该领域成为领导者。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12268087289/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第三、美国错误地估计了5G</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">事实上，早在多年前，美国就开始规划5G网络的频谱，例如在2016年，美国就推出了关于5G网络频谱的文件，并在之后的2017年和2018年，都推出文件积极地采用毫米波频段。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">也就是说，在美国的规划中，就自然地认为5G将会直接进入毫米波频段，而不是像4G网络那样，也会工作在Sub-6GHz频段。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">然而这种错误的估计其实还不止如此，5G网络不仅会工作在Sub-6GHz频段，而且在初期的5G网络，还会工作在NSA模式上，也就是说，核心网还会采用4G网络，无线网部分才会是5G基站。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9663338571/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第四、美国错误地估计了自己的影响力</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">从时间上来看，美国在5G网络的规划和部署上确实是比较早的，或许也正是因此，美国要尽早的确定其采用的5G频段，以达到一种类似“业界标杆”，或者说“风向标”的作用。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">其目的在于，美国希望可以引领全球的5G建设方向，让其他国家的5G建设也同样采用毫米波频段，不仅可以避免美国的频谱尴尬，还能刺激美国在该领域的商业发展，可以说是一举两得。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">但不得不说，事实证明，美国错误地估计了自己的影响力，虽然美国在3G、4G网络上具备一定的技术优势，但显然市场并不会盲从，而是有着自己理智的判断，结果美国成了5G上的孤家寡人。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">根据媒体的报道，虽然美国也开始采用中频段建设5G网络，但是这来之不易的100MHz频谱，其本来的用途其实也是供应军方，显然在5G网络的商用建设上，美国最终还是做了二选一的选择。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/11630062780/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这是一次华为的成功</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">通过上文的分析，我们应该已经看出，在此之前，美国是高频毫米波频段的积极拥护者，但是在这方面，华为则坚持无线网络发展的阶梯性，而不是跨越性。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">简单来说，无线网络的发展需要一步一步走，美国在5G网络上选择跳跃Sub-6GHz，而直接进入6G网络才会起步采用的毫米波，是不现实的。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这次美国在5G建设上调转船头，以不惜让军方让步的代价，积极推进在中频段的5G网络，很显然，这无疑证明了华为对于无线网络发展的预判是正确的。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">但更加关键的在于，美国此举让全球看到，在无线通信领域，谁是内行，谁是外行；谁是专家，谁是笑话；谁更可信，谁更可疑；以及谁更能提供有价值、有竞争力和有质量的5G技术。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10431972203/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">要想向全球去证明自己有多么优秀，这无疑很难，但美国用自己做了一个完美的反面教材，将华为在5G上的能力衬托的淋漓尽致，因为在最基本的5G发展方向上，华为对了，而美国错了。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这无疑是美国5G规划部署上的一次重大失误，但确切的说，这标志着美国在5G上已经大溃败。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">美国5G已经大溃败</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">从最开始，美国就已经错了，但却一直错的理直气壮和沾沾自喜，直到现在认清了现实，但对于现在的美国5G来说，其实已经处在了大溃败的状态。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">美国作为大国和强国，我们并不能将其去与一些落后国家相比，例如如果将美国的5G去与非洲的某些落后国家去比较，那根本没有可比的必要了，因为很多国家4G都还没有普及。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">所以美国5G的大溃败，自然是与当今的世界强国和大国来比较，主要集中在以下几个方面。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12268087515/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第一、时间上已经落后</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">上文中我们已经提到，只有美国采用毫米波建设5G，目前全球已经商用的5G网络已经有近百张，很显然，大部分商用的5G网络，都是采用的中低频段，而美国在中频段的5G网络，连频段的分配都还没有解决。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">事实上，根据媒体的报道，虽然这次美国痛下决心，要开始建设中频段的5G网络，但是该频谱资源要到2021年12月份，才能开始进行拍卖，而开始使用这些频谱则将会推迟到2022年的夏天。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这无疑在时间上，就已经落后了约三年左右，三年时间是什么概念，按照我国目前建设5G基站的速度，基本上是一周建设一万站以上，按照三年来计算，我们就能够建设至少超过150万个5G基站。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9332504256/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第二、技术上已经落后</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这一点想必没有异议，美国拒绝采用华为的先进设备，但华为在5G技术上的领先性已经毋庸置疑。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">首先任正非之前就已经表示，华为的技术领先其他国家两到三年，但金一南在一次节目中指出，华为的技术领先欧洲四到五年，英国电信方面就曾经宣称，华为是全球唯一一家真正的5G供应商。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">而英国沃达丰也曾经表示，如果禁用华为，那么将无法确保英国在5G领域的领先地位。同时英国军情六处处长扬格直言：5G技术主要是以华为技术为基础。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">很显然，华为5G技术的领先性已经得到业界的认可，但美国却没有采用。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/11777643639/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第三、基础设施已经落后</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">5G网络建设不只是设备的简单更新，核心网换成5G的，无线基站换成5G的，就完成5G网络的建设了？就完成网络的升级了？事情并没有那么简单。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">这方面任正非之前也已经提到过，5G网络的建设，需要作为基础设施的光纤铺设到位，这就提及了光纤覆盖率的问题。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">以中国为例，我国光纤的覆盖率早就超过了90%，而美国则远低于中国这个数字，任正非表示，美国要想建设先进的光纤网络，需要投入数千亿美元。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">事实上，美国即便想要提高光纤的覆盖率，其实也很难，这不仅仅是钱的问题，光纤的铺设就要涉及土地的使用，但美国存在土地私有化的问题，大量的土地是属于私人的，如果“地主”不同意，事情很难办。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9908506506/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第四、频谱资源依然匮乏</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">在文章开始的时候，我们已经提到，美国在中低频段的资源匮乏，这些资源都已经被美国军方所占据，这次分配出来的100MHz，也是军用和商用二选一之后的结果，可见其频谱资源的匮乏程度。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">但是即便是这100MHz频谱，其实也是捉襟见肘，目前美国有三大电信运营商，这也就意味着，这点可怜的100MHz频谱，也要被三家来瓜分，那么每一家能够分到的频谱资源就更少的可怜。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">作为对比，我们不妨看看我国在频谱资源上的划分，例如中国移动，在2.6GHz频段上，拥有160MHz的频谱资源，在4.9GHz频段上，拥有100MHz的频谱资源，而中国联通和中国电信，在3.5GHz频段上，都拥有100MHz的频谱资源。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">所以在频谱资源上，彼此的差距就有好几倍，但还有一个问题，我国的频谱是分配的，所以频谱都是连续的，而美国的频谱要拍卖，这就很难保证频谱的连续性。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">碎片化的频谱会降低5G网络的质量和速度，但巧合的是，在处理频谱碎片化上，华为拥有全球最强的技术，而事实上，也只有华为可以很好的处理频谱碎片化的问题。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/11003512936/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">第五、技术工人匮乏</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">想必大家也都知道了，因为5G网络的工作频率更高，所以基站的覆盖面积变小，因此覆盖相同的面积，就需要建设更多的5G基站才行。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">但这又面临着一个新的问题，建设基站需要相应的技术工人，根据今年年初的数据显示，美国当时只有2.7万名技术工人，但美国在此基础上，还需要再增加10万名技术工人才能满足需求。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">培养一个技术成熟和工作熟练的技术工人，在短期内是难以实现的，即便在工人的数量上达到了要求，在质量上也很难短期达成目标。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">所以我们整体来看，美国在5G网络的建设上，人不够用，技术不先进，基础设施匮乏，频谱资源匮乏，最后建设时间还晚了这么多，这难道不是美国5G的大溃败吗？更严重的问题在于，以上提及的这些问题，并不是说砸钱就能短期解决，甚至砸钱都无法解决。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10977091398/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">写在最后</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">然而就在近日，华为方面则表示，5G网络建设已经告一段落，下一阶段是聚焦5G的商用，释放5G的红利。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">也就是说，5G的发展，已经从5G网络建设发展到5G网络应用，开始进入到利用5G网络实现经济价值的时代。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">很显然，美国在5G上的溃败，已经不仅仅是5G建设上的溃败，更是5G应用和对国家经济发展的溃败；美国对5G的错误估计，也已经不是5G网络建设程序的错误估计，更是5G对提升国家竞争力的错误估计。</p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">总之，就5G而言，华为是成功的，而美国败得一塌糊涂。</p>', 3, 1617244991);
INSERT INTO `__PREFIX__wwh_news` (`id`, `newscategoryid`, `newsname`, `n_keywords`, `n_description`, `summary`, `tjdata`, `image`, `weigh`, `time`, `content`, `views`, `updatetime`) VALUES
(11, 3, '华为“塔山计划”不是为手机准备的，而是为了保5G', '关键字1,关键字2,关键字3', '说明演示文字11', '有媒体爆料华为正在实行“塔山计划”，预备建设一条完全独立自主的45mm生产线，华为要自建芯片制造厂，完成EDA、材料、制造和封测全产业链的贯穿。', '1', 'http://demo.wuwenhui.cn/uploads/20200909/a75205d88b0ad7b3887bac4ad254043a.png', 1, '2020-09-09', '<p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">有媒体爆料华为正在实行“塔山计划”，预备建设一条完全独立自主的45mm生产线，华为要自建芯片制造厂，完成EDA、材料、制造和封测全产业链的贯穿。但很快，华为就紧急辟谣了，所谓的“塔山计划”是子虚乌有。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">看到这条消息，我有两个想法：即使没有“塔山计划”，但华为肯定也在积极准备其他类似的计划，自建芯片制造工厂，是华为躲不开的一条路；华为的芯片工厂，不是为手机准备的，而是为5G准备的。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">下面，我们就这两个方面来展开讨论：</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">第一，为什么自建芯片制造工厂是华为的必然选择？</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">本来就全球产业趋势来看，芯片设计和制造分开是大势所趋，也就是人们常说的IDM/Fabless/Foundry模式之争。IDM集芯片设计、芯片制造、芯片封装和测试等多个产业链环节于一身，英特尔、三星、德州仪器（TI）属于这一类。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">Fabless（无工厂芯片供应商）模式只负责芯片的电路设计与销售，海思、高通、英伟达、AMD、联发科（MTK）、博通等都属于这一类，剩下来的芯片制造环节则交给台积电这样的Foundry（代工厂）完成。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">从正常的产业趋势来看，这一设计、制造分离的模式符合技术潮流，英特尔把部分芯片制造交给台积电也印证了这一趋势。因为芯片制造资本投入太大，先进制程的竞争也需要大量的研发投入。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">然而，由于美国的打压，扰乱了这一正常的产业发展逻辑，让华为不得不发展芯片制造工业。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">华为自建芯片工厂，有必然性也有可能性。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">必然性。不仅台积电靠不住，就连中芯国际也靠不住。首先，中芯国际最先进的量产工艺是14nm，而且产能肯定有限，无法满足华为手机动辄上亿的芯片需求。14nm工艺，对于强调性能的手机，完全就“不能打”，会严重拖华为手机的后腿。中芯国际为代表的中国芯片代工制造厂现在已经处于事实上被制裁状态，由于得不到EUV光刻机，它的技术上限已经被美国锁死在7nm。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12270938203/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">更重要的是，中芯国际不仅没有帮助华为的能力，而且他也没有帮助华为的意愿。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">中芯国际CEO梁孟松于近期表示，由于要遵守美国的制裁法律，在9月14号之后也不能为华为发货了。还声称将会有其他客户代替华为的位置，进入中芯国际的产能。这很明显，中芯国际选择自保，与华为做切割。其实这也不能怪中芯国际，因为他自己也严重依赖美国的技术和设备，如果因为华为而受到美国制裁，那他自己会很快停摆。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">放眼全球其他代工厂，三星跟台积电一样也靠不住，而国内其他芯片代工厂会面临中芯国际一样的问题。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">留给华为的就只有“自古华山一条路”——自建芯片制造工厂。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12270938204/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">需要指出的是，华为自建芯片工厂，并不是工厂里的所有设备都要自主研发，这是根本的不同。即使自建工厂，绝大部分设备肯定还是要购买的。就目前形势来看，华为完全可以通过各种途径采购到相关的半导体设备。美国现在也没有明文禁止华为“自己使用美系设备为自己生产芯片”，而且可以从日本、韩国、欧洲进口相关设备。退一步说，目前国产半导体设备的国产化也在快速推进，只是制程上还比较落后。比如30nm以上制程的相关设备，除了光刻机外，其他环节已经有很多突破了。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">一个半导体工厂投资动辄几百亿，需要一两年时间。但华为完全可以先建一个小规模的工厂，再慢慢进行技术升级和扩建，建厂的资金成本和时间成本都会小很多。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12270938205/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">第二，华为自建半导体工厂，一定是制造5G基站芯片，而不是手机芯片。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">手机芯片有两个特点，一个是制程要求高，另一个是产量需求大。手机芯片的性能要求很严格，面对安装了7nm甚至5nm芯片的智能手机，那些装14nm以上芯片的手机完全没有竞争力。面对性能严重落后的华为手机，即使在国内，消费者也很难买单。而且，华为手机每年的销售量上亿，对芯片需求巨大。华为即使自建半导体工厂，要提升到如此量级的产能水平，也必然需要很长一段时间，远水解不了近渴。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">华为手机芯片，目前只能通过外采的方式来满足需求。短期来看是联发科会承接华为的芯片需求，长期来看高通也很可能给华为供货。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">前不久，高通就向美国政府申请继续向华为供货，并警告称出口禁令不会阻止华为获得必要的组件，反而会把每年80亿美元的市场拱手让给其海外竞争对手。高通认为，获得与华为交易的许可将为公司带来数十亿美元的收入，并有助于为新技术的开发提供资金。反之，不但便宜了其海外竞争对手，对华为也“几乎没有影响”。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">早在2019年2月7日，美国白宫科技政策办公室（OSTP）发布《美国将主导未来产业》，这一文件被称为“史上最强工业计划”，把人工智能、先进制造、量子科技、5G四大关键技术领域视为美国的“基础设施”。其中5G将成为中美竞争的焦点，特朗普还专门制定了《国家频谱战略》来推动其发展。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12270938206/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">美国打击华为的重点是5G和芯片，这是他们一定不会妥协退让的。即使将来高通可以为华为手机供货，美国也一定不会放开对华为5G的限制。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">与手机芯片相比，5G基站芯片更适合自建工厂来制造。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">(1) 采购5G芯片比手机芯片更加困难。5G是美国的打击重点，肯定不会放开对华为5G的封锁。华为即使想外购5G芯片，也会受到诸多限制。而且，5G基站芯片的供应商本来就很少，技术还都没有华为先进。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">(2) 5G基站芯片的需求量更小，自建一个年产能百万量级的晶圆厂就可以满足需求。手机芯片需求量数以亿计，这需要很庞大的产量水平。而5G基站的数量则小很多，今年我国5G基站规模不会超过100万，未来几年也会在百万量级，总共的5G基站需求量不会超过1000万。建立一个年产量几百万的芯片工厂，难度比建年产量几千万甚至上亿的工厂要小得多，投资规模也会小很多。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">(3) 5G基站芯片对制程的要求更低。手机芯片由于对于性能的需求更强烈，7nm以上的芯片就很难有竞争力了。5G基站由于体积比手机大很多，芯片也可以做的更大，即使是30nm制程也勉强可以接受。华为自建工厂，其制程水平肯定比台积电差很多，甚至赶不上中芯国际的14nm水平，但这在5G基站领域已经勉强够用了。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">相信华为肯定储备了大量的5G基站芯片，但储备再多也总有用完的一天。即使储备了足够3年使用的芯片，那5年以后呢？</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">买芯片就像买鸡蛋，而自建一个芯片制造工厂就像买了一只会下蛋的母鸡。虽然鸡蛋没那么好吃了，但总归不会饿死。假如储备的芯片够华为生存3年，那一旦建成一个芯片工厂，华为可以再多活5-10年。那个时候，中国半导体设备产业也慢慢跟上来了，日子就会更好过一点。</span></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12270938207/1000\" class=\"content-picture\" style=\"margin: 0.6em auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; display: block;\"></p><p class=\"one-p\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 2em; padding: 0px; line-height: 2; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Avenir, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;微软雅黑&quot;; font-size: 14px;\">所以，华为内部一定是在积极筹备芯片制造工厂的，至于叫“塔山计划”还是其他计划倒无所谓。但有一点，华为的芯片工厂多半是为5G准备的，而不是为了手机。</span></p>', 0, 1617244997);
